PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of NARMIN ISMAIL-TEJA of Calgary, Alberta, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of History, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective January 2, 2019, in the place of Robert C.
